OL,3,CSecurity failings found in wake of
OL,4,Calleged Wandsworth prison escape `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FAn audit found a raft of security
OL,8,Ffailings at a scandal hit jail after a
OL,9,Fprisoner allegedly escaped, according
OL,10,Fto a report.
OL,12,FHMP Wandsworth's Independent
OL,13,FMonitoring Board (IMB) said a security
OL,14,Faudit identified "81 points of
OL,15,Ffailure" and resulted in "long
OL,16,Foverdue" upgrades being made to CCTV
OL,17,Fcameras which had not worked for over
OL,18,Fa year.
