OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FDaniel Khalife is accused of fleeing
OL,8,Fcustody in September last year while
OL,9,Fbeing held on remand over spy charges.
OL,10,FHe allegedly strapped himself
OL,11,Funderneath a food delivery lorry and
OL,12,Fwas arrested a few days later. The
OL,13,Fformer soldier denies all the charges
OL,14,Fagainst him and is due to stand trial
OL,15,Fin October.
