OL,7,FEarlier this month the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice (MoJ) announced it would be
OL,9,Fredirecting #100 million from across
OL,10,Fthe prison service to spend over five
OL,11,Fyears on bringing in "urgent
OL,12,Fimprovements" as well as sending in
OL,13,Fextra specialist staff after the full
OL,14,Fdetails of Mr Taylor's inspection were
OL,15,Fpublished, laying bare a "shocking"
OL,16,Flevel of chaos at the prison with
OL,17,Fstaff unable to "account for prisoners
OL,18,Fduring the working day".
