OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe latest findings from the IMB,
OL,8,Fpublished on Thursday, described
OL,9,FWandsworth as a "failing prison" which
OL,10,Fwas "constrained by staff absence and
OL,11,Fhindered by underfunding and lack of
OL,12,Fsupport from the prison service".
OL,14,FIts report said the alleged escape led
OL,15,Fto multiple reviews and action
OL,16,Fincluding "previously unavailable
OL,17,Ffunding" being made available for
OL,18,Fsecurity improvements and "significant
OL,19,Finvestment" in a bid to stop "illicit
OL,20,Fitems" being brought into the prison.
