OL,7,FThe extra funding allowed "long
OL,8,Foverdue" upgrades and repairs of the
OL,9,Fprison's "antiquated" CCTV systems,
OL,10,Faccording to the IMB. This included a
OL,11,Fnew system installed in May this year
OL,12,Fin the visits hall to replace an old
OL,13,Fsystem "which had not been functioning
OL,14,Ffor over a year".
OL,16,FThis "immediately led to an increase
OL,17,Fin the number of illegal passes
OL,18,Fdetected".
