OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe IMB's annual report for 2023-24
OL,8,Fconcluded the prison ` which is since
OL,9,Funder new leadership ` was "not safe",
OL,10,Fwith close to 1,000 assaults recorded
OL,11,Feither between prisoners or on staff,
OL,12,Fand it was "alarmingly easy" for
OL,13,Fprisoners to get hold of contraband
OL,14,Fwith cell searches finding phones,
OL,15,Fdrugs, makeshift weapons and alcohol.
