OL,7,F"The recently released report from His
OL,8,FMajesty's Inspectorate of Prisons was
OL,9,Fhighly critical but said little that
OL,10,Fsurprised us. Many of the same issues
OL,11,Fhad been raised in previous IMB annual
OL,12,Freports and ignored by the Ministry of
OL,13,FJustice".
OL,15,FPreviously Mr Taylor described his
OL,16,Finspection of Wandsworth as
OL,17,F"catastrophic" and symbolising the
OL,18,F"problems that characterise what is
OL,19,Fworst about the English prison system".
