OL,7,FHe told how security remained a
OL,8,F"significant concern" at the prison
OL,9,Fbut said failings were "evident in
OL,10,Falmost all aspects of the prison's
OL,11,Foperation" as he highlighted how an
OL,12,Faction plan made in the wake of the
OL,13,Flast escape in 2019 had not been
OL,14,Fcompleted and that prior to the latest
OL,15,Falleged incident "security procedures
OL,16,Fhad been neglected for a considerable
OL,17,Ftime".
