OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe security audit resulted in the
OL,8,Fprison being handed the lowest grade
OL,9,Fof unsatisfactory and while there was
OL,10,Fa "clear vision" of what was needed to
OL,11,Faddress concerns, the "pace of
OL,12,Fimprovement was slow", he said.
OL,14,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "The new Government inherited a
OL,16,Fjustice system in crisis and has been
OL,17,Fforced to take action and get a grip
OL,18,Fof the situation across the prison
OL,19,Festate, so we can lock up dangerous
OL,20,Foffenders, protect the public and make
OL,21,Fprisons safer for hard-working staff.
